\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}There were a few plugins that I considered. If I were to make the decision about which to purchase, I would most likely download demos of the top 3 choices and see which were most intuitive and powerful. However, my assignment was to pick one somewhat quickly, so I choose 
\b Leaky Paywall 
\b0 ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zeen101.com/leakypaywall/"}}{\fldrslt https://zeen101.com/leakypaywall/}}).\
