\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sl360\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl2\cf2 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}I chose this plugin because it appears to be updated often and has had positive reviews by several review sites. The fact that it is an established product with a support staff tells me that if there are problems, there would be somewhere to turn. It is worth the money, to me, to know that I am getting a secure, maintained product.\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}I like especially that it follows a metered paywall model \'97 this has been effective in the past for gaining my business \'97 it allows content to be shared on Facebook and other social media sites even if it is behind a paywall. I know that for some services, content behind a paywall is completely hidden so will get less attention despite being premium content.\
{\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}There are several features and methods to customize service for both the subscriber and the business. This would give RNS the ability to try different models and choose the one most effective for them as opposed to having to guess beforehand.\
