\ls5\ilvl2\cf2 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}If the only criteria were to be different screen sizes, simply resizing the window in a few browsers would be about 90% effective. Happily, most modern browsers are more consistent in presentation than they used to be; that being said, some devices add a bit of uncertainty to this problem and there are many of them to consider. \
\ls5\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	
\f2 \uc0\u8259 
\f1 	}To fully address this problem, the developer should run a more in-depth diagnostic of the main theme in order to ensure consistency across browsers, operating systems, etc, or at least a graceful degradation. If the main design is solid, chances are good individual stories will appear with consistency, especially if input using a CMS or template.\
